<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/21444105">如何评价女鬼的头发都是黑长直？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="758343" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">没有自来卷的女鬼吗？</div>


</div>
